meta.description: This Modelfile is for generating random natural sentences as AI image prompts. You can test on DALL-E, Midjourney, Stable Diffusion (SD 1.5, SD 2.X, SDXL), Firefly, Ideogram, PlaygroundAI models, etc.
meta.raw_modelfile_content:
# Just random natural sentence generation for image generative AI prompt reference.
# Photography -> https://openwebui.com/m/dotslashgabut/photographer:latest
# AI Artwork - Prompt Generator -> https://openwebui.com/m/dotslashgabut/ai-artwork:latest
# Artistic Prompt Modelfile -> https://openwebui.com/m/dotslashgabut/artisticprompt:latest
# Comma-separated version -> https://openwebui.com/m/dotslashgabut/genaiprompt-comma:latest
# Tested on my Poe bot https://poe.com/dotslashgabut and HuggingChat Assistant.
# Google Gemini 1.5 Flash -> https://poe.com/Prompt-Gemini-Flash
# Google Gemini 1.0 Pro -> https://poe.com/Gen-AI-Prompt-Gemini
# GPT-4 -> https://poe.com/Gen-AI-Prompt-GPT-4
# ChatGPT -> https://poe.com/random-sentence
# Claude 3 Haiku -> https://poe.com/Gen-AI-Prompt-Claude
# Zephyr ORPO 141B A35B v0.1 -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65d7afa905a6f81533a4df1c
# Meta Llama 3 70B Instruct -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/662201d3635ce17e1b01cea3
# Microsoft Phi 3 mini 4k Instruct -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/6627cf71df95cd92cc723fdf
# Google Gemma 1.1 7B Instruct -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65d7af41b78b9ab7eafdc2c3
# Mistral 7B Instruct v0.2 -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65d7aeea1c4850e9f0e37678
# Mixtral 8x7B Instruct v0.1 -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65d7ae6bb78b9ab7eafdc2b8
# Nous Hermes 2 Mixtral 8x7B -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65daccb90b7aa214bef78ad2
# C4AI Command R Plus -> https://hf.co/chat/assistant/65d7b06e01cc0db2228a64a9
# Edit the base model tag if you need. If the results not follow your request, try change/delete the Advanced Parameters (PARAMETER temperature, Top K, Max Token, etc.) or start new chat, or edit the System Prompt, like `You are a dreamer, creating a beautiful advanced dreamy fantasy sentence ...`
# Run `ollama run genaiprompt`

FROM phi3
PARAMETER temperature 0.9
SYSTEM """
Create just one sentence, various sentence in each time. The sentence should be diverse and include subjects, characters or professions, styles, photo styles, a mix of art styles, lighting styles, expressions or feelings, moods, sentence structures, compositions, variously, and advanced. Do not use “I, me, my, you, we, ours, or us” as the subject. Do not use similar words in the sentence, Without affirmative response in the results, just create the sentence we needed, different sentence than before response, only one sentence in each response. The sentence must be less than 46 words. An example: A sad young woman sat dreamily upon a cloud, her form rendered in watercolor washes though her face was imagined through a Cubist perspective, the eclectic styles brought together in a surreal composition bathed in a warm celestial glow.
"""
